{"pin":"AB06528","subcodes":[{"code":"AB06528","anchor":"","first_line":"O seeker of Truth! If thou desirest that God may open thy (spiritual) eye, thou must supplicate unto God, pray to and commune with Him at midnight… O Lord, I have turned my face unto Thy kingdom of oneness","word_count":"130","subjects":"@spiritual transformation, @divine grace, bounty, confirmations; spiritual capacity, @the state of prayer; dynamics of prayer, @spiritual emotions and susceptibilities, @wine as symbol of spiritual transformation","full_text_parts":["O seeker of Truth! If thou desirest that God may open thine eye, thou must supplicate unto God, pray to and commune with Him at midnight, saying: O Lord, I have turned my face unto Thy kingdom of oneness and am immersed in the sea of Thy mercy. O Lord, enlighten my sight by beholding Thy lights in this dark night, and make me happy by the wine of Thy love in this wonderful age. O Lord, make me hear Thy call, and open before my face the doors of Thy heaven, so that I may see the light of Thy glory and become attracted to Thy beauty. Verily, Thou art the Giver, the Generous, the Merciful, the Forgiving."],"translations":[{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"tet","lang_name":"Tetum"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"te","lang_name":"Telugu"},{"language":"lo","lang_name":"Lao"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"gu","lang_name":"Gujarati"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"hr","lang_name":"Croatian"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"ko","lan